show.description: On her wedding day, An Ran is betrayed by her fiancé and family — and loses everything, including her life. Reborn with vengeance in her veins, she forces her enemy’s rival into marriage to begin her path of revenge. But as love unexpectedly blooms, An Ran must choose between justice and the new future she never saw coming.
